text:
DDoS attack on official dedicated servers continues since January 2024.
You have 5 choices:
1. [strike]Play[/strike] Suffer on official dedicated servers with 900+ ping;
2. Play on modded community servers;
3. Play on modded hosted servers (and it will download on your computer some shitty or MALWARE (very rare) addons);
4. [strike]Play[/strike] Suffer offline with stupid vanilla bots;
5. Uninstall Left 4 Dead 2;

Thanks for nothing, [strike]CEDA[/strike] Valve.
